{"tid":2455920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美日防長據報確認台灣出現突發事態時密切合作，菅義偉稱自衛隊今後或被賦予新任務","createTime":"2021-03-21T13:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T16:46:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e0523a6d55e2df95cb19db01abccc4d4cb5235","tid":2455920,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:31:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581725-20210321.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581725-20210321.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=6bd4cd18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581725-20210321.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2b215e3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581725-20210321.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國防部長奧斯汀日前訪日，與日本防衛相岸信夫舉行會談。共同社報道，雙方關注台海可能發生不測事態，岸信夫更指出，日本與台海地理位置較近，和平與穩定將受到很大影響，認為今後有必要探討自衛隊，能為前往支援台灣的美軍，提供甚麼協助。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述日本政府消息指，把台灣突發事態作為會談議題的要求，由美方提出，雙方一致認為局勢緊張加劇或導致武力衝突，確認在台灣出現突發事態時密切合作。<br />\n<br />\n報道又說，日本政府內部暗中認定台灣突發事態，屬於若放任不管，恐將發展為對日直接武力攻擊的重要影響事態，正探討能否發出命令，保護美軍艦船和飛機。美方在會上未有提出具體應對措施。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，國台辦發言人早前表示，台灣問題是中國內政，不容任何外來干涉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581724-20210321.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581724-20210321.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=77f3550d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581724-20210321.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e4bf49f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581724-20210321.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n日本首相菅義偉表示，自蘇聯30年前解體以來，安全環境出現重大變化，認為自衛隊必須學會在這種環境下行動。<br />\n<br />\n菅義偉在神奈川縣橫須賀市出席防衛大學畢業禮時又說，未來可能會出現前所未有的挑戰和威脅，自衛隊可能被賦予新的任務，希望大家願意嘗試新事物，以應對未來的變化。<br />\n<br />\n菅義偉又談及預計下月訪問美國的行程，表示決心加強同盟關係，並建立與美國總統拜登的私人信任關係，強調再無任何一個國家，能夠獨自保障自身和平與安全。"},{"pid":"2fb331914e9e865d6c0f46242c33ccd732511dab","tid":2455920,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:29:58.000Z","msg":"自衛隊正名軍隊<br />\n日軍來了我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b50a9e82dd751f4044e45bffa9b78c39bcb082","tid":2455920,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:36:25.000Z","msg":"如果美國解放日本有核武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ba2ad1782e8c9500dbebf009af8e5d81c4d81f","tid":2455920,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"日本搞返軍隊中國會唔會驚到賴屎"},{"pid":"ec741f52385464d95d86423d525d7a5559415f23","tid":2455920,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tOAd1bh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtOAd1bh.gif&h=e833a85f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1fZm94E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1fZm94E.gif&h=6fe90826&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44def81a9197fa762c7bdfe2392aff4095d1984b","tid":2455920,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"小日本亡我之心不死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}